name: The Peach Tree Story
description:
The PeachTree Story

It's a fantasy little world with magic, you are a little girl who wish to grow up.

This day is a fresh day, you heard that the village cheif is calling you.

You pick up your sword, for the first time you want to face the world and maybe be a shero.

This is a game I made in 20 weeks for study. @MSio helped with buildings, bridge, boat, street light and statu. voice over : @MSio--Shushi, @Lanyouzi--the girl, Luke--village cheif. Background music from: https://opengameart.org/content/snowland-town Wind: https://bigsoundbank.com/detail-0908-wind-in-tall-grass.html Holysound: https://opengameart.org/content/another-space-background-track Tailer background: https://www.newgrounds.com/audio/listen/814473 All the 3D animations in this game are come from maximo! Unity assets : Fantasy Skybox FREE, WaterProDaytime

It's a small game with some part unfinished.

Sorry if the voice over is too bad for you ^ ^

Thanks if you like it.
